Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么又到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.50,up,,0,0,0,,调查还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:17.09,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1348,859)\c&HE6F9FE&}冬木市圆藏山部分崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.21,up,,0,0,0,,今早警察在进入现场的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.54,up,,0,0,0,,寺里的建筑崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:16.46,up,,0,0,0,,现在为大家带来从现场发来的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.84,up,,0,0,0,,我现在位于冬木市深山町圆藏山的柳洞寺前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.64,up,,0,0,0,,山门前就像这样已经拉起了警戒线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber小姐这次回国真是太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.98,up,,0,0,0,,已经看不到里面的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.27,up,,0,0,0,,此次的房屋崩塌的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.27,up,,0,0,0,,是这座柳洞寺里的池子周边一带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 前辈晚上也就不用再出门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不会遇到危险的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是我陪着Saber外出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是我让Saber跟着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从此以后可能我不在家的时间会更多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 希望你不要因为我回来晚而一直在大门口等着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该战胜的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还在这座城市里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.64,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H31BBFC&\3c&H274BD0&\bord3\blur3\fax0.35\frz333\fad(0,200)\move(980.933,370.334,980.933,400.334)}冬木入口
