Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,新都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,中央公园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个像影子一样的家伙到底是什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,和脏砚又是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是在控制它？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,又或者只是在利用它？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,需要去问一下远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 还活着呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的名字好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫士郎 卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 士郎 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是敌人吗 伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Master只能在晚上战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来和士郎聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你呀 之前突然向我砍过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么好聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀 才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是都怪士郎这么弱还挡前面来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是现在我也是能杀掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有Saber的士郎 轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微陪陪我可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅你是住在森林里的城堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉和利兹和我在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是瞒着塞拉偷偷地跑来见士郎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感到荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我还能再问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫切嗣这个名字听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有些话想和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要聊在学校也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer 去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？ 不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始作战会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要快点准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你早说啊 樱发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是远坂你不让我插嘴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二 放开樱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放心好了 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀卫宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只是要给他一点苦头尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,与Rider打一场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能平安结束你想说什么我可以奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,上 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果还想继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就不应该只身一人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这么容易翘掉 那就太没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐力真强 算你胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错 不需要再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider 就这样杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.86,anotation3,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\c&H365B7F&\frz141\fax-0.35\pos(352.8,699.8)}社会与发展心理学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,给我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,远…远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我和卫宫签订了合作条约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你利用了樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是彻底与我为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 樱 樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 樱 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这种家伙无所谓的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当上Master的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这废物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样把他们全杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐的血脉已经断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,已经无法降生出能够使用魔术的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为是脏砚召唤出Rider交给慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是事实却单纯得多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的间桐家 最符合做Master的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐的正统后继人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这一代的魔术师 是你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,樱是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,令咒的转让
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“听从间桐慎二的指示”的令咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个原因 慎二成为Rider的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在此期间你会失去作为Master的权限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就变成普通的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们眼睛往哪儿看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为是创造了令咒的间桐家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,才有可能实现这样的作弊方法 对吧 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,重新再来一次 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次 把支配权给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还装什么乖宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,令咒还有一画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快用那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了令咒 Rider便会获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你即使作成了伪臣之书 也会被立即烧毁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用借来的令咒驱使Servant的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,从一开始就不是Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 我知道的 我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情从一开始就知道我不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,换你来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,替我杀了他们 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是哥哥先毁约的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明明答应不杀前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是不能控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,离这里远点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,随随便便为她提供魔力 后面可就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,退下 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的主人正在失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话会魔力消耗殆尽自取灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只要吸取更多的魔力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,即使换了主人你还是本性难移吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,结界！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,够了Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我 不是要你做这种事才召唤你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能遵从这项命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,比起任何事物 我会将你的性命置于第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 石化之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:22:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:23:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,樱！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,终于醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚治疗完间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.27,0:24:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,樱她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.61,0:24:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我和Rider把你们带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.26,0:24:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,绮礼 樱的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管还没有安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.41,0:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少命是保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.79,0:24:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的魔术刻印怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在对间桐樱的治疗上不得不全都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 就是这次的治疗结果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.48,0:25:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,刻印虫？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想象成活着的魔术回路就行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.78,0:25:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被刻印虫附上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.20,0:25:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就会渗透进身体一切角落
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不断吸收精力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.62,0:25:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,用粘液刺穿皮肤 浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后与你共用快乐中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,通过让中枢崩溃来获得满足感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.22,0:25:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,被这种虫子侵蚀的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.39,0:25:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,无论身心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,两者都会被侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.68,0:25:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,以至崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.31,0:25:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐樱也同样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.77,0:25:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为说明还是有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.07,0:25:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只要那个还在身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.28,0:26:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,作为生命活力的魔力会被无止境地汲取
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定活不长久
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.83,0:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,手术不是成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.58,0:26:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,十一年份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.46,0:26:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,强行取出的话身体会先承受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.88,0:26:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,完全去除只能依靠圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.79,0:26:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,作为冬木的管理者
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.95,0:26:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要对她进行制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.92,0:26:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是指间桐樱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.84,0:26:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对于无法驾驭力量的魔术师不能让她活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.76,0:27:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经是发了疯的Master了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.98,0:27:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,即使…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.81,0:27:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的亲妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.82,0:27:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂家本来是有两个孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.41,0:27:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是魔术是独子单传
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.13,0:27:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,由我继承了远坂的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.92,0:27:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,樱则作为已经断绝血脉的间桐 玛奇里的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.97,0:27:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过继给他们当养女抚养
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.68,0:27:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.43,0:27:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我和樱是亲姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.69,0:27:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们互相一次都没有这样叫过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.61,0:27:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.32,0:27:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就更应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.49,0:28:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是将她放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.70,0:28:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,又会发生今天一样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.67,0:28:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下次会被陌生人出手干预 毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.67,0:28:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,动手杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.42,0:29:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,从珍视的人那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.66,0:29:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,得到宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.97,0:29:53.64,anotation,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\b1\fax0.45\fry25\pos(1035.2,564.2)\frz274.3\c&H0D1743&}施工中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.66,0:30:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要比远坂先找到樱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.54,0:30:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.08,0:30:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了樱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.83,0:30:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我又能…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.21,0:30:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.05,0:30:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上不应该是要战斗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.57,0:30:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎已经不是Master了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.98,0:30:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我全部都知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.56,0:30:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider的Master倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.98,0:30:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩下两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.03,0:30:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎想去救Rider的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是找不到她是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.91,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 都快要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.88,0:31:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.18,0:31:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.05,0:31:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.93,0:31:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我站在士郎这一边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.91,0:31:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这一边？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今早说的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.90,0:31:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣的事 其实我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.07,0:31:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的降生是为了圣杯战争取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而我作为伊莉雅的目的是要杀死切嗣与士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.29,0:31:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.00,0:31:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎要是想保护重要的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.38,0:31:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我 就是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,保护喜欢的人是理所当然的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.47,0:31:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.79,0:32:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这下真的连一个可以回的家都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.98,0:32:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.94,0:32:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.74,0:32:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.45,0:32:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.45,0:32:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.70,0:33:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,感冒 还没好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.04,0:33:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.92,0:33:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚的那个 并不是什么有毒的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.25,0:33:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只是让感觉更敏感的药而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.26,0:33:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就只是因为这点刺激而迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.14,0:33:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让前辈受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.31,0:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那一点 对我不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.73,0:33:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是间桐家的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.07,0:33:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来都对你有隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.86,0:33:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有告诉樱我当上了Master的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.61,0:33:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来前辈家里 也是因为害怕 不敢反抗爷爷的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.66,0:33:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上说着帮前辈 一直以来都在骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.21,0:33:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.13,0:33:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我这种人不配待在前辈身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:34:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以之前的种种都到今天结束 从明天起便装作陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.44,0:34:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,走廊里遇见也要擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.69,0:34:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,放学后也要装作陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.40,0:34:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人乖乖回家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.53,0:34:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,想把一切的一切都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.49,0:34:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.20,0:34:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,比想死的时候拿刀抵着手腕还要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.13,0:34:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欺骗前辈的时候是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.09,0:34:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在放弃一切的时候也同样害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,周围都是可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.59,0:34:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我一步也无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.89,0:34:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.64,0:34:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我今后也想守护与前辈之间的点点滴滴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.19,0:34:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对我 对我而言 只有那才是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一有意义的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.84,0:35:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言珍视的人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.37,0:35:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不想让她再继续哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.43,0:35:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何人责骂樱
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.10,0:35:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,使得樱她只能自己责骂自己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.10,0:35:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就应该牵起她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.56,0:35:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,带她来到阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.15,0:35:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,即使所有人都不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也会代替你 不断地原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.54,0:35:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.05,0:36:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚樱是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.26,0:36:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知什么时候会像刚刚那样失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.60,0:36:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一定又会做出无法挽回的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.40,0:36:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的我哪里还会有容身之处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.62,0:36:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 就是你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.54,0:36:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.80,0:36:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.13,0:36:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是处女了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.93,0:36:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,初体验早就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.10,0:36:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.28,0:36:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从那次以来就一直被莫名的东西摸遍全身
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.02,0:37:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有受到前辈保护的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.83,0:37:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我来守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.83,0:37:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.79,0:37:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你想自我了断
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都会来保护樱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.46,0:37:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,前…辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.18,0:37:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要成为属于樱一个人的正义伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.02,0:37:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.11,0:37:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 前辈你一定会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.32,0:37:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明明会受伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.12,0:37:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.98,0:38:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.61,0:38:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.44,0:38:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.09,0:38:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.10,0:38:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想守护至今为止的信念的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.02,0:38:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那样倒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.56,0:38:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还能够预见到未来的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.56,0:39:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果选择完全不同的路
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.36,0:39:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎不会有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.11,0:39:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.63,0:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,累了吧 好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.18,0:39:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.81,0:39:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为长时间淋雨发烧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.69,0:39:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.98,0:39:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.53,0:39:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.95,0:39:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么是我能帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.20,0:39:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.50,0:40:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.83,0:40:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.21,0:40:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不 只要给我一点点血就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.42,0:40:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.47,0:40:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.56,0:41:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.16,0:41:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.58,0:41:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.91,0:41:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,继续玷污前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.48,0:41:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 先把海带煮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.95,0:41:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,菠菜要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.37,0:42:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天用芝麻拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.08,0:42:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 鸡蛋给我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.17,0:42:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.64,0:42:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一起吃饭感觉真有些怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.77,0:42:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.77,0:42:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.90,0:42:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不需要像你们人类一样摄取营养
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.95,0:42:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 Saber倒是经常吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.66,0:42:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不习惯你们的用餐方式
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.83,0:42:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.84,0:42:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.02,0:43:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,关于今后的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.27,0:43:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让樱获胜 并让她使用圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.56,0:43:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 樱你还是不要离开家里
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.61,0:43:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟直接遇见脏砚是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.91,0:43:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的想法是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.28,0:43:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.62,0:43:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算如何打败那位魔术师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.62,0:43:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为应该与其他Master合作
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.75,0:43:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩下哪几个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.97,0:43:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂的Archer 樱的Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.35,0:43:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚指挥的Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.80,0:43:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 伊莉雅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.60,0:43:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.86,0:43:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.28,0:43:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.70,0:44:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 注意不要离开家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.46,0:44:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.84,0:44:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,后悔什么的 事到如今已经来不及了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.38,0:44:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider 要是遇到危险 就把前辈带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.97,0:44:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.52,0:44:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为真正值得注意的不是那个老人 而是那位神父
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.15,0:44:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢 我其实也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.24,0:44:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.91,0:44:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.04,0:44:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那个人是赢不过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.83,0:44:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.51,0:45:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前…辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.90,0:46:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦 只要不去外面不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.20,0:46:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 就不会遇到危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.97,0:46:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.42,0:46:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.93,0:46:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.86,0:46:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这路可真是难走
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.00,0:47:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是让我跟着它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.22,0:47:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.77,0:47:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.69,0:47:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.19,0:48:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你也和你主人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.49,0:48:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.91,0:48:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,完全感觉不到要跟我们战斗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.70,0:48:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么在乎自己的性命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.04,0:48:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.34,0:48:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愿望是长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.67,0:48:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看呀 我这幅肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.47,0:48:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,每时每刻都在腐烂 散发出腐臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.72,0:48:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不停地失去所积累的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.60,0:48:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这种疼痛 活生生地腐烂的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.60,0:48:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你能懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.52,0:48:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不存在不畏惧死亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.49,0:48:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果说我的愿望能因此而实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.33,0:49:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意一个一个地杀死全世界上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.34,0:49:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对你无语了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.76,0:49:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然迷失到了这种地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.26,0:49:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玛奇里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.18,0:49:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请回想起来 我们的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.60,0:49:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到达奇迹的渴望自何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.77,0:49:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为何 想要以一个普通人的血肉之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.94,0:49:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,到达凡人无法到达的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.62,0:49:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,区区个人偶却说却得挺像回事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.97,0:49:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对祖先的模仿都已经完全烙印在心里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.75,0:49:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,玩笑开就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.51,0:49:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦的圣杯就由我间桐脏砚收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.42,0:50:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.15,0:50:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.61,0:50:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.11,0:51:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到 卫宫也在考虑和我一样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.57,0:51:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.79,0:51:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.54,0:51:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,被那东西打倒的话就没办法回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.52,0:52:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看来胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.19,0:52:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.06,0:52:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别眼睁睁地被爱因兹贝伦的女儿溜走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.66,0:52:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.96,0:52:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.19,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer 你也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.78,0:53:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.63,0:53:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的对手 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.55,0:53:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.81,0:53:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.50,0:54:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.89,0:54:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,纯洁的英灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.47,0:54:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是无法抵抗这个诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.52,0:54:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你就跟这个森林里的冤魂没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.15,0:54:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.89,0:54:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.97,0:54:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.02,0:54:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.14,0:55:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker————
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.58,0:58:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.88,0:59:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.25,0:59:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,后面交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.92,0:59:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢 我去把之前的失策补救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.18,0:59:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.74,1:00:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.59,1:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.30,1:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你 是多余的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.44,1:00:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不靠偷袭 你连小孩的脑袋都砍不掉吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.73,1:00:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,三流
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.82,1:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么还能在这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.41,1:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.87,1:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.70,1:00:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.58,1:00:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,被那玩意追上就完了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.05,1:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,回头再问罪
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.51,1:01:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 快点跑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.47,1:01:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,既然握住了伊莉雅的手 你就要保护她到最后
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.73,1:01:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.25,1:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.47,1:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你还能动
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.01,1:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.22,1:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不像其他人那样是正统的英灵
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.64,1:01:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,既然不纯洁 就能够容许一定程度的污秽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.02,1:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 这幅身躯本就是扭曲的英灵
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.09,1:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.63,1:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以变回灵体了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.43,1:02:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧从这里…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.85,1:02:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.81,1:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.99,1:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.07,1:02:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.87,1:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马上跑 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.51,1:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力汇聚起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.80,1:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子下去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.47,1:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.61,1:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,此身为剑所成
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.61,1:03:28.70,small,,0,0,0,,I am the bone of my sword
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.61,1:03:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,钢铁为身
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.61,1:03:31.99,small,,0,0,0,,Steel is my body
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.53,1:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,纵横无数战场而未尝一败
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.53,1:03:38.00,small,,0,0,0,,I have created over a thousand blades
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.63,1:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,炽天覆七重圆环
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.63,1:03:47.17,small,,0,0,0,,Roll Aeneas
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.67,1:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.48,1:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.60,1:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.93,1:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.73,1:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.91,1:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,保重啊 远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.22,1:05:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.94,1:05:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦这样做了 你就会…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.19,1:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不用考虑
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.61,1:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果什么都不做那就会有两个人消失
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.20,1:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这么做就会有一人得救
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.92,1:05:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.51,1:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊 变成这样自然会吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.85,1:06:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,受了一点小伤
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.52,1:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一层层缠着 看着是很夸张
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.65,1:06:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是什么严重的伤
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.86,1:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在那碰到远坂了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.36,1:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她救了我 暂时休战
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.44,1:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 这位是伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.37,1:06:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,事出突然真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.25,1:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,樱？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.34,1:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊能动吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.09,1:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.22,1:06:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是 人类移植Servant的肢体实在是太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.91,1:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.18,1:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你使用这条胳膊 哪怕一次
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.39,1:06:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer的魔术回路就会启动
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.11,1:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,并且他的魔术构成会使你的身体承受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.32,1:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,从内部产生崩溃
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.95,1:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那这些布是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.66,1:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是封印
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.45,1:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.75,1:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这么突然 你干什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.34,1:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就打算帮你直到打倒脏砚为止的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.13,1:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 有在她身边我也方便
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.05,1:07:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有在考虑樱的事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.35,1:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了不是那样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.48,1:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我如果没当上Master的话 和你就不会有瓜葛了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.15,1:07:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这可有些不对哦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.95,1:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你怎么想 我很久以前就认识你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.54,1:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是四年前左右吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.88,1:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你直到太阳落山都在练习助跑跳高 有过这事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.51,1:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时在场
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.89,1:08:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,明明做不到 我傻傻地眺望着这个不愿放弃的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.14,1:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果认定我做不到 那便会彻底放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.94,1:08:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人生性冷淡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.94,1:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我好歹也是魔术师
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.91,1:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生这样下去好吗 就在这么想的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.87,1:08:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了和自己完全相反的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.79,1:08:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好震惊的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.60,1:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不许夺走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.52,1:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要连这份回忆…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.11,1:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都夺走
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.84,1:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定只要摘掉这布 会恢复原样了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.79,1:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.92,1:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这可…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.96,1:09:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.56,1:10:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.31,1:10:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,樱的幸福就是有你陪在她身旁
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.61,1:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外她都不需要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.57,1:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望她能活下来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.95,1:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.17,1:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 你是站在樱这一边的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.80,1:10:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今后 不管遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.27,1:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.27,1:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,樱？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.11,1:11:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 魔力不足了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.36,1:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,进来先等会
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.37,1:11:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小刀 我放哪了来着
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.48,1:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.11,1:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈你…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.11,1:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.82,1:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,保护我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.62,1:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.33,1:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话想要对你说
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.17,1:12:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.59,1:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,与你分开根本无法想象
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.14,1:12:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是将我当作家人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.06,1:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.23,1:12:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当作女人？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.36,1:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.53,1:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢樱
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.54,1:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.12,1:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.38,1:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.97,1:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.72,1:12:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,肮脏吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.81,1:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪…吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.02,1:13:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.56,1:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是来到前辈的房间
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就会这样
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.65,1:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人再怎么自慰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.86,1:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有办法平息
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.49,1:13:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中…只有前辈了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.49,1:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.87,1:13:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这么下流
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.67,1:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.38,1:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点也不下流
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.92,1:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,樱你很美
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.93,1:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.71,1:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.46,1:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.59,1:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才姐姐只是带着前辈离开一会儿
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.47,1:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.88,1:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.98,1:14:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.45,1:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.08,1:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.29,1:14:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,辈…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.55,1:14:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.27,1:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.27,1:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.74,1:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.66,1:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.04,1:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.25,1:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,正在诞生的另一个圣杯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.84,1:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她是 由某个在众人手中诞生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.55,1:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,却不被众人所接受的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.01,1:15:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,名为 世间一切之恶所孕育
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.85,1:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是善恶之所在
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.35,1:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说并非是得到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.43,1:15:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而是要使能够作答之人诞生的话
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.85,1:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.23,1:15:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,答案已经很近了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.75,1:16:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,假如这个疑问亵渎了神明
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.78,1:16:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那便立于神前
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.87,1:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奉上全心
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.50,1:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,将吾主一同消灭
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.38,1:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,既然寄人篱下 至少早饭要让我来做
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.14,1:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我去给远坂前辈打下手
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.36,1:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.74,1:16:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.28,1:16:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 对远坂…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.37,1:16:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 做点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.29,1:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 我先洗一下这边的菜
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.17,1:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.30,1:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是有些奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.31,1:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.89,1:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪什么的完全没有啦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.95,1:17:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅 关于那件事情去我的房间谈好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.58,1:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事情是什么事情
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.83,1:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也需要一两个秘密武器的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.20,1:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer的手臂之中可蕴含着爱因兹贝伦家的知识哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.42,1:17:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我向远坂提议 是否有办法把它利用起来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.85,1:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我个人是对基修亚・泽尔里奇的遗物不感兴趣啦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.27,1:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟是魔法使留下的宝箱 肯定很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.98,1:18:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,基修亚・泽尔…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.49,1:18:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.66,1:18:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.92,1:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,过去一直都只是远远地看着
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.13,1:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到能叫“姐姐”的这一天真的会来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.51,1:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,自从去了间桐家 就没再和远坂有过交流吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.22,1:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我和姐姐都只是知道我们是“姐妹”这一事实
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.81,1:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,互相之间一直尽力避免交流
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.65,1:18:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果我的魔术被她知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.61,1:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会讨厌我的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.53,1:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.25,1:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐家的术式 原本就是限定于从他人处夺取的魔术
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.96,1:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,仅是一味地夺取 从不教授他人喜闻乐见之事
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.30,1:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,樱你 讨厌间桐的魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.31,1:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,确实训教非常严格
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.40,1:19:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但要说到刻苦 绝对比不过前辈你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.32,1:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈你在晚上在做什么样的修炼 我有看到过
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.78,1:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾多次想要阻止
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.91,1:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈的修炼是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.09,1:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像要亲手刺破自己的喉咙一般
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.72,1:19:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,况且这不是受他人强迫
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.26,1:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直独自一人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.22,1:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,固执地坚持着
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.18,1:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们几个之中 前辈你一定是最强的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.90,1:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是因为魔术特性
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.28,1:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为拥有一颗纯粹的心
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.96,1:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,自相遇的那一刻起 我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.38,1:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人一定…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.88,1:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是个不会背叛的人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.27,1:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是你夺走的 卫宫
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.88,1:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.09,1:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.09,1:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没发生啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.81,1:21:29.57,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1573.334,833)\c&H766C5E&\shad1.5\4c&HD4D4D4&\1a&H00&\4a&H00&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.20,1:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,继续播报下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.32,1:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,于冬木市新都的中央公园内
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.78,1:21:32.11,up,,0,0,0,,发现了疑为杀人事件受害者的遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.65,1:21:33.53,up,,0,0,0,,被害者为4人…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.36,1:21:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快看这里
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.20,1:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,杂草变成了黑色
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.16,1:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说…是那个影子干的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.16,1:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是脏砚下的指示吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.51,1:21:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.21,1:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得他会留下这样的证据
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.71,1:21:47.71,up,,0,0,0,,警方正在展开搜查
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.75,1:21:50.34,up,,0,0,0,,下面为您播报明天的天气
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.67,1:21:52.55,up,,0,0,0,,气象预报中心 佐藤主播
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.97,1:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.76,1:21:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有味道诶
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.77,1:22:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.98,1:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.69,1:22:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还能感受到
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.78,1:22:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,时间要是停在这一刻 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.16,1:23:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,轻快地散着步
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.04,1:23:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,空空的脑袋晃晃悠悠
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.87,1:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,将满满当当的目标计划全都抛诸脑后
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.13,1:23:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摇摇晃晃 向前进
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.80,1:23:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,微微笑哼唱着 向前进
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.55,1:23:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,空空的手脚像纸气球一样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.43,1:23:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在地面上咕噜咕噜地滚啊滚
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.22,1:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想要在天上轻飘飘地飞 要等长大以后
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.06,1:23:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,向前进
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.48,1:23:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,向前进
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.98,1:23:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,向前进
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.14,1:24:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁走了过来 咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.85,1:24:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,又是谁在发笑 嘻嘻哈哈
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.91,1:24:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不记得邀请过你们
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.46,1:24:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们叮叮当当吵闹作响
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.30,1:24:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,空空的肚子叫了起来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.90,1:24:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,胃口真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.40,1:24:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那时候才叫你赶紧去死
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.97,1:25:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一闪一闪的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.39,1:25:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的缓期已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.06,1:25:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就作为我给你的最后一点慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.83,1:25:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.12,1:25:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还能有一口气
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.09,1:26:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是影子 居然连身体都开始变化了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.70,1:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然想让我跪下
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.82,1:27:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你这孽畜
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.26,1:27:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.43,1:27:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,成长到这等…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.75,1:28:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂你看到没
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.72,1:28:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.37,1:28:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.53,1:28:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧来客厅
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.17,1:28:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今日二十二点左右
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.34,1:28:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,新都站周边发生了大范围停电
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.22,1:28:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,同时接到像邻居消失 失踪 突然间消失等大量离奇报案
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.77,1:29:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.15,1:29:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等着 我去拿医疗道具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.61,1:29:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.62,1:29:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别去多想
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.79,1:29:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.30,1:29:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,相似什么的 不能去想这些
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.22,1:29:40.14,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6752&\bord0.2\blur1\fs50\move(1325.334,699.667,1373.334,699.667)\3c&HFFFFFF&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.14,1:29:42.10,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6752&\bord0.2\blur1\fs50\move(1373.334,699.667,1413.334,699.667)\3c&HFFFFFF&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.10,1:29:43.52,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6752&\bord0.2\blur1\fs50\move(1413.334,699.667,1433.334,699.667)\3c&HFFFFFF&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.52,1:29:44.81,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6752&\bord0.2\blur1\fs50\move(1433.334,699.667,1447.334,699.667)\3c&HFFFFFF&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.81,1:29:45.94,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6752&\bord0.2\blur1\fs50\move(1447.334,699.667,1450.334,699.667)\3c&HFFFFFF&}新都中央公园内发现大量遗体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.72,1:29:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,仅根据当前统计 遇难者已经超过了60人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.85,1:29:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能确定住户去向的建筑现已达到40栋
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.73,1:29:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,樱她…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.74,1:29:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.78,1:29:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.66,1:30:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.62,1:30:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,樱的身体 只是看上去接在了一起
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.21,1:30:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上手脚的肌肉都断裂了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.34,1:30:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.63,1:30:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,确确实实地死过一次了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.55,1:30:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说不知道是被谁弄的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.35,1:30:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是破坏身体带来的痛苦 还可能涉及大脑
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.14,1:30:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,必须尽早打败脏砚和那个影子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.65,1:30:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为此要尽我们所能
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.07,1:30:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.12,1:30:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.37,1:30:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说脏砚和那个黑影毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.12,1:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.81,1:31:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.35,1:31:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还保留着自我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.60,1:31:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.10,1:31:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里吸收的这么多灵魂
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.52,1:31:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明明Assassin和Rider尚存
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.78,1:31:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你就已经快溢出来了 真是让人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.33,1:31:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.74,1:31:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道接下来你会变成什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.21,1:31:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.25,1:31:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我究竟会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.42,1:31:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会死哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.88,1:31:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没救
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.10,1:31:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.89,1:31:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微回来一小会儿
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.19,1:31:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 你不在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.28,1:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呀
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.99,1:32:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.84,1:32:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎到底去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.87,1:32:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在小樱这么难受的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.25,1:32:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.21,1:32:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.59,1:32:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对我说会保护我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.05,1:32:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.68,1:32:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.23,1:32:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.39,1:32:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,破坏了前辈的梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.44,1:32:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.15,1:32:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.82,1:32:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.20,1:32:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.24,1:32:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎是个见到不好的事情就会训斥的人哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.22,1:32:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱也…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.63,1:32:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,想着要改正自己不好的地方的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.17,1:33:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.18,1:33:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 士郎的梦想是成为正义的伙伴对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.24,1:33:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有想保护的人 不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.27,1:33:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是指…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.44,1:33:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对大家平等的保护
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.56,1:33:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果士郎的目标是切嗣的话
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.06,1:33:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有重要的人也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.28,1:33:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣他也是有所偏袒的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.41,1:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自从在这个城市住下后
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.38,1:33:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣他去了国外很多很多次
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.59,1:33:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,直到…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.01,1:33:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不能动弹为止
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.06,1:33:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.35,1:33:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有无论如何都想见的人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.56,1:34:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不能见到重要的人是非常痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.03,1:34:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,正义的伙伴也不例外
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.28,1:34:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.79,1:34:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小樱一定要陪在士郎身边哦
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.48,1:34:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.19,1:34:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.49,1:34:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的自己吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.75,1:34:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.25,1:35:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说这是背叛的话
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.20,1:35:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.59,1:35:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊——
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.82,1:35:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.65,1:35:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.24,1:35:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.20,1:35:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.25,1:35:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术师阁下想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.68,1:35:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,比我预想的来得早啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.69,1:36:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫家的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.98,1:36:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.44,1:36:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的只有一句
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.78,1:36:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在立刻解放樱
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.24,1:36:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,解放吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.20,1:36:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.62,1:36:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.13,1:36:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天喊你来是有事相求
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.30,1:36:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老夫想让你去把那个黑影杀掉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.43,1:36:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西和你是一伙的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.01,1:36:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一伙的…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.97,1:36:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得和那东西能沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.23,1:36:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从昨晚开始 已经连安抚都做不到了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.40,1:36:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 在此之前 先得告诉你那个黑影到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.66,1:36:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,非要说的话 那是圣杯的内容物
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.54,1:37:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从圣杯这扇门里喷涌而出的意识 那便是黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.96,1:37:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,黑影与…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.72,1:37:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,门
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.97,1:37:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说要你杀掉黑影 但是这想必是非常困难的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.27,1:37:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.27,1:37:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以杀死门
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.35,1:37:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老夫 以及远坂家的女儿想必也已经察觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.19,1:37:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant只是单纯的饵食罢了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.16,1:37:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.33,1:37:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,被埋下了圣杯的碎片
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.70,1:37:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老夫培育了十年的间桐家的圣杯 能杀死她的只有…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.44,1:37:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.01,1:37:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定已经注意到了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.18,1:37:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个东西和樱非常相像
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.52,1:38:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只伫立在那里的人偶
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.15,1:38:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能死在自己心爱之人的手中
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.69,1:38:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是得偿所愿了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.53,1:38:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.99,1:38:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,樱的意识一旦淡薄
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.97,1:38:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,潜意识中借用她身体的圣杯就会浮上表面
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.41,1:38:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,将会重蹈十年前的覆辙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.34,1:38:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想拯救樱的话
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.13,1:38:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就要忍耐到圣杯战争结束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.76,1:38:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,根据以往的情况来推算
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.93,1:38:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大概还有4天吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.27,1:38:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.56,1:38:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得樱撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.98,1:38:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,撑得住 肯定撑得住
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.65,1:38:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 其他人可撑不住
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.78,1:39:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为昨晚暴饮暴食 现在它的肚子可能还不饿
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.87,1:39:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到了明天 那东西又会出动
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.00,1:39:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市的人被吃完 会花几天呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.22,1:39:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你是明白的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.72,1:39:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,代表万民 铲除邪恶
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.93,1:39:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想继承卫宫切嗣的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.64,1:39:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐樱才是…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.90,1:39:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你真正该对付的敌人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.71,1:39:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.06,1:40:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.02,1:40:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.04,1:41:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 你…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.75,1:41:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等这场战斗结束后 有什么想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.93,1:41:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想不到什么想做的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.26,1:41:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和前辈在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.60,1:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.06,1:41:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.35,1:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.82,1:41:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.62,1:41:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.07,1:41:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去…赏花
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.20,1:41:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.00,1:41:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么说定了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.18,1:42:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,用冷酷的心去编织一个温暖的幻想
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.19,1:42:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,待冬天过去
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.90,1:42:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,春天到来的那一天
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.11,1:42:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.91,1:42:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去赏樱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.47,1:42:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.26,1:42:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等到春天到来…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.60,1:42:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.52,1:43:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.61,1:43:01.44,up,,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.53,1:43:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从珍视的人那里得到宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.32,1:43:03.82,up,,0,0,0,,我要成为
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.82,1:43:06.66,up,,0,0,0,,正义的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.07,1:43:06.78,up,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.32,1:43:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,和前辈在一起的时间 要是能一直维持下去
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.12,1:43:11.70,up,,0,0,0,,要是停在这一刻 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.78,1:43:11.37,small,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.37,1:43:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.04,1:43:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.79,1:43:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.95,1:43:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.16,1:43:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,辈…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.96,1:44:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要背叛自己吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.47,1:44:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.76,1:44:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.18,1:44:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你带给了我许许多多
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.18,1:44:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.27,1:45:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能喊你姐姐 真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.77,1:45:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,藤村老师
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.86,1:45:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.69,1:45:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有遵守承诺
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.16,1:45:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.45,1:45:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.25,1:45:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你没有杀前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.88,1:45:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.26,1:45:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后的令咒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.27,1:45:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.48,1:45:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.82,1:45:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷就由我来阻止
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.78,1:45:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.70,1:45:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能再给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.37,1:46:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.54,1:46:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.86,1:46:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 叛徒
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.36,1:46:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回来的够晚啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.29,1:46:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.08,1:46:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.46,1:46:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.58,1:46:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你拿着
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.92,1:46:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.89,1:47:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.44,1:47:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,樱真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.99,1:47:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.70,1:47:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,会超越远坂吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.38,1:47:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.13,1:47:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.01,1:47:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是嚣张
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.27,1:47:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明明只是我的人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.11,1:47:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我又错了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.78,1:47:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会遭受如此过分的对待
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.03,1:47:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.07,1:48:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和平时一样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.66,1:48:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,忍忍就过去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.00,1:48:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.54,1:48:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.21,1:48:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.38,1:48:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.88,1:48:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.80,1:48:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.39,1:48:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经是前辈的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.76,1:48:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.02,1:48:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被调教得这么乖了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.85,1:48:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.02,1:48:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.36,1:48:38.28,up,,0,0,0,,你倒是再反抗试试啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.53,1:48:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么总会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.40,1:48:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我很早以前就这样想
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.24,1:48:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我很早以前就这样怨恨着
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.45,1:48:44.62,up,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.83,1:48:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我周围的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.79,1:48:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是如此地…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.50,1:48:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,厌恶我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.38,1:49:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去告诉卫宫
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.64,1:49:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,迄今为止 你是有多么依赖我
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.48,1:49:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是有多么淫荡地和我上床
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.40,1:49:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.40,1:49:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果消失了那该多好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.72,1:49:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.26,1:49:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.61,1:50:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,樱——
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.88,1:55:57.09,anotation3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,720)\fs80\fad(300,1500)}下 回 预 告
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.67,1:55:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.42,1:55:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成为樱一个人的正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.22,1:55:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.76,1:56:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,咬紧牙关
